import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { ActivatedRoute } from '@angular/router'; import { IShopLikeDislike } from '../shop-like-dislike.model'; @Component({ selector: 'jhi-shop-like-dislike-detail', templateUrl: './shop-like-dislike-detail.component.html', }) export class ShopLikeDislikeDetailComponent implements OnInit { shopLikeDislike: IShopLikeDislike | null = null; constructor(protected activatedRoute: ActivatedRoute) {} ngOnInit(): void { this.activatedRoute.data.subscribe(({ shopLikeDislike }) => { this.shopLikeDislike = shopLikeDislike; }); } previousState(): void { window.history.back(); } }
